  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with Sand</h2>\"Sand in a Box\" is a dynamic falling sand simulator where you play with various materials like sand, water, salt, acid, and many others.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thermal Imaging View</h2>Explore the heat dynamics in your simulations with a thermal imaging view. This feature helps you understand the flow of heat between different materials.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electrical Conductivity</h2>Harness the power of electricity in your sandbox. Conduct electricity through metals and observe its interactions with other materials, such as boiling water with an electric heater.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Radioactivity</h2>Experiment with radioactive materials. Observe the half-life decay of elements and their impact on surrounding materials.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modding Capabilities</h2>Enhance your gameplay with modding support. Create and share your own custom elements. Modify the game rules to your liking and explore new possibilities through a community-driven platform.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Play with Sand</h2>\"Sand in a Box\" is a dynamic falling sand simulator where you play with various materials like sand, water, salt, acid, and many others.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/f9fd20de6b430d29a1516d8e7e721a62.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Thermal Imaging View</h2>Explore the heat dynamics in your simulations with a thermal imaging view. This feature helps you understand the flow of heat between different materials.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/0798b86d7936736275ef04de9922617a.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Electrical Conductivity</h2>Harness the power of electricity in your sandbox. Conduct electricity through metals and observe its interactions with other materials, such as boiling water with an electric heater.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/d5777f99e2791b3ebbc1bb5e07df2989.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Radioactivity</h2>Experiment with radioactive materials. Observe the half-life decay of elements and their impact on surrounding materials.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/881729aaf0b6f97c0f9a9fc04060b365.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Modding Capabilities</h2>Enhance your gameplay with modding support. Create and share your own custom elements. Modify the game rules to your liking and explore new possibilities through a community-driven platform.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.poster.avif?t=1732027750\" width=616 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.webm?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2225680/extras/4178193d81e0042a3760d63438dc3bf6.mp4?t=1732027750\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
